Description:
Award medals are an outstanding way to recognize any job well done. &nbsp;TrophyPartner.com offers an extensive selection of medals for all sports and activities.&nbsp; We offer die cast medals, insert medals, custom medals, dog tags and much more.&nbsp; Each recognition medal includes a free neck ribbon in your choice of color, sport, or activity.<br />
<br />
We offer medals in all sizes and shapes from value priced to premium. &nbsp;Can't find the award medal you are looking for or want to create your own?&nbsp; We offer an extensive selection of custom made award medals. &nbsp;Contact us for more information or browse our custom medals section to see all of the exciting options. &nbsp;&nbsp;

Mascot Award Medals make the perfect option to recognize your school spirit.&nbsp; We offer Bulldog, Pirate, Ram, Tiger, Lion, Eagles, Panthers, and Cougar award medals so you can truly show your school spirit.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
<br />
Each award medal features the option to add artwork and text to the back.&nbsp;&nbsp;

Eagle Trophies make the perfect corporate recognition award. &nbsp;Few things match the grace and power of the flight of an eagle. &nbsp;The majestic eagle trophies we carry represent characteristics such as independence, stamina, commitment, and freedom. &nbsp;Choose one of our eagle awards to celebrate employee of the month, achievement of a particular goal, or excellence.<br />
<br />
TrophyPartner.com carries eagles in flight, soaring eagles, American Eagles, eagle mascots, and many more. We include 60 free characters of text on each trophy and free ground shipping when you purchase over $300. &nbsp;

Technology Awards recognize those individuals and businesses that create the information technology necessary to run our companies.&nbsp; Examples include Hackathon Trophies, Best Technology Solution, Best Management Solution, Best eCommerce Solution, Best Payments Solution, Best Data Platform, Best Compliance Solution, and a host of others.<br />
<br />
TrophyPartner.com carries a wide variety of stock crystal awards and acrylic awards in a variety of sizes and budgets, but we can also develop a <a href="https://www.trophypartner.com/t-customawards.aspx" title="Custom Awards">custom award</a> program for you as well integrating your company, logo, and objectives.&nbsp;&nbsp;
